name: Scouser poster — Cyan (Movember)
description:
A print inspired by Harry Enfield's legendary sketch, 'The Scousers' with all profits being donated to my personal Movember challenge this year for the The Prostate Cancer Charity.

What is Movember?
Movember (the month formerly known as November) is a moustache growing charity event held during November each year that raises funds and awareness for men's health.

Size: 420mm x 297mm
Print: 300gsm digital matte (non glossy)

This item will be dispatched worldwide within a sturdy hardback envelope to avoid creasing. (Postage and packaging are included in the price).
